 PutPlayer(X(PL),RealY(PL)+Y(PL)+PILE*15,AN(PL),SIDE(PL),PlType(PL),PL,0)

 ' CALL A SOUND EFFECT IN A SINGLE GAME LOOP
 IF PLSFX(PL)>0 THEN PLAY_SAMPLE PLSFX(PL),PL: PLSFX(PL)=0

